metadata.name: In Faith
metadata.description:
Ordinary photographs of my turkey Harriet has lead to a vast array of unexpected imagery that always existed right before me. This image in particular has a powerful story behind it of faith that has reminded me that we are never alone throughout any trials in life.

Not only is this image a symbol of hope, but turkey feathers are also symbolic of bringing abundance and pride. May this piece of artwork hold all of these elements for its NFT 1/1 owner.
